# Design System — Screen Wakelock Detector

Before editing UI in `app/`:

1. Read [`docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md`](docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md)
2. Theme tokens: `app/src/main/java/com/screenwakelock/detector/ui/theme/`

## Mandatory rules

- **`androidx.compose.material3` only** — never Material 2
- Dynamic color API 31+; static fallback 29–30
- User-visible strings in `res/values/strings.xml` — use `stringResource`, not `Text("...")` literals in composables
- Accessible touch targets and content descriptions per DESIGN_SYSTEM.md
- Expressive M3 APIs opt-in only; never block release on alpha

## FOSS Android

- No `com.google.android.gms`, Firebase, or proprietary SDKs
